rComments: Amazingly nice, sweet guy! He would always help me when I was confused about something, and make sure I understood it. It is great having a prof who came from the country they teached, and Mr. Ohm was passionate about Germany and would tells us lots about Germany. He did stick to the text too much and spoke mostly English, but overall he's great!<3

Professor Ohm is a fantastic instructor and by far my favourite professor in first year. He explains all concepts concisely, is enthusiastic and passionate about the German language, and cares deeply about his students. It was an absolute pleasure being in his class and every day, I looked forward to the lectures. Just an awesome prof.
